{"type": "article", "id": 10437, "title": "“挂帘”灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:29:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235630bpQxUCrWywLuKMAk.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Arik Levy 推出了一款“挂帘”灯饰，其设计意在把气氛性照明设备与空间分隔系统结合起来，使得不管是开灯还是关灯，这款产品都能起到自己的作用。目前由三款不同型号的灯，分别是上横梁LED灯具，下横档LED灯具，和一款上下均配备横档的LED灯具，三款灯可以由不同的方式排列组合，在不同场合的使用。这是 <a href=\"http://www.ariklevy.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Arik Levy 设计工作室的官方主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235626QvSMZrukPs3peTw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235627jULPIKJz3gQiCxZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235627vP2mwFAxhB0cyqDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235627BW7tPA3LqavJGZNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235628hnRWCx1OXdSi2TBA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356286XKoPWeV48JASO23.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235629Y9EJz12xHm5Uouar.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235629uzP6OmpdiRVo8rDl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}